<section class="legacy-section">
    <div class="legacy-content">
        <h1 data-i18n="sports_legacy_title">Tharlam Sports Association</h1>
        <p data-i18n="sports_legacy_description">
            A core part of the **Tharlam Monastery's** commitment to holistic
            development, the Sports Association offers multiple programs,
            fostering **teamwork, discipline, and healthy living** among our
            students. Our primary goal is to nurture both academic and athletic
            potential within the monastic community.
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="join-button">
            <span data-i18n="sports_legacy_cta_text">View Our Programs</span>
            <span class="arrow">&rarr;</span>
        </a>
    </div>
